Class UserManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • UserManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class UserManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The UserManager class stores a list of all of the users. userMap stores every username along with its associated User.
